Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law finally clash with Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Law's secret motive behind this fight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can take you \Nall down with this power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the Op-Op Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gives you the ability to\Nmodify human bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can perform miraculous operations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand cure even unknown diseases with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, we'll get a jump on Doffy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the others and steal the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coming to Minion Island along with Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon raided the hideout \Nof the pirate - Barrels{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and managed to steal the Op-Op Fruit.\NHowever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:17.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NO SOUND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got it, Law! It's the Op-Op Fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your disease will be cured!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?! He freaked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A guy in a black coat \Nstole the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:05:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Moment of Resolution!\NCorazon's Farewell Smile!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:19.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SWALLOW ISLAND - THE RENDEZVOUS POINT OF\NTHE DONQUIXOTE FAMILY ¬Å~ CORAZON
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down.\NOur enemy is Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sengoku, that fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TSURU\NA VICE ADMIRAL OF THE NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he get the information
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,to deploy us like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Vice Admiral Tsuru!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call from the look-out ship\Nat Minion Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:55.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,MINION ISLAND\NTHE ISLAND WHERE THE PIRATE BARRELS HIDES
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:55.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Barrels' hideout is on fire?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Some of us are heading\Nto see what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once they find you guys,\Nthe deal will be off!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Check the coastal area now\Nand tell me if you see someone suspicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:42.61,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE GHOST TOWN\N THE PIRATES' HIDEOUT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Barrels!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about my wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a five-billion berry deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. You are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's the Op-Op Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The building is on fire and I heard some gunshots
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought maybe something happened to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's beside the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Devil Fruit will save your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I eat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't know if it will cure my disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NIt will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, eat it! Here! Eat it quickly!\N--What are you doing...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Chew it like this!\NChew it up and swallow it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NI wasn't even ready to become a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Devil Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}? H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can... cure yourself now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have outsmarted Doflamingo...\NWe won...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}?\NAre you just tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're covered in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}, did you get shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I made a little blunder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!\NWhat are you doing, Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get better! Get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get better!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop bleeding! Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Op-Op power! Heal him!\N--That's foolish of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you the ability doesn't work like magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:10:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... got shot because of me,\Ndidn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's not like that...\NI just messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law... I'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These wounds won't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to stanch the bleeding\Nfor a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sure did get the Op-Op Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't stop\NDoflamingo running wild yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to use you when you're weakened
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I need you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a Navy look-out ship\Noff the west coast of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to hand this over to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Navy soldiers will know what it is\Nonce they see this cylinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one small package will save...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a far-off kingdom called Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kingdom? But I hate the Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the son of a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to save more than just sick people from now on, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so bent out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you finish delivering this,\Nlet's get off of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's travel all around the world,\Njust you and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Navy soldiers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's all by himself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it must be a secret letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet somebody asked you to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, little boy,\Nyou sound so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if you're talking about the letter,\NI'll take responsibility and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to help someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He got shot and he's dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to die at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got shot... because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he's gonna give you first aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Corazon?! What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you just talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no! Don't tell me his secret mission is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo... Is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vergo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a strong man who's currently separated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nfrom the Family on a secret mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The details of the mission have been kept secret even from the Family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no business with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Vergo's mission is to infiltrate the Navy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How unlucky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are thousands of Navy soldiers\Nand of all of them, he got the letter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Rosinante!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosinante!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You! You! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Vergo guy, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.61,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vergo guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess\Nyou're Law from the White Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about you.\NI heard you two went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no sense of propriety!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that I'm your great {\i1}senpai{\i0}, you call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Vergo-{\i1}san{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.02,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote down\Na fair amount of information in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Navy got this kind of letter,\Nthat'd be it for the Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise for our future plans and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the kid more important to you\Nthan the Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we had a rat like you in our Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were eight, you went missing one day.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you came back to us again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...14 years later!\NIt was enough to be skeptical about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But merely because you're his brother,\NDoffy didn't distrust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know what's coming,\Nshouldn't you, Rosinante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...\NCora-{\i1}san{\i0}... He's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Vergo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa-whoa,\Nyou haven't killed them, have you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still breathing... \NJust barely though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Corazon was the Navy's spy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he was with the Family in order to frame you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful. They must know all of your plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now, Doffy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the rendezvous spot, Swallow Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from a distance earlier and two warships came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I became convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My once-lovely young brother shows me his teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it reminded me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you guys are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the only "family" I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, what I thought was true, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just landed at\NMinion Island where you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a bit too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We arrived and saw Barrels' underlings
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,running around saying the Devil Fruit got stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Corazon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he's there, don't let him go anywhere!\NHe has the Op-Op Fruit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! Those fools...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, did they run?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, no worries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're in the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! Something's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on\Non this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--These strings are like blades!\N--They're solid, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}, what happened to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where is Vergo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of Doffy's abilities, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it before but\Nthere's one thing I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody! Stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using the Parasite String in the cage, huh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, this is like hell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cora-{\i1}san{\i0}, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can let Law get away, just him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no chance to survive now but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will you remember me even after I die?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll die with a smile so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because... if you think of me someday,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd rather you remember my smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, we gotta get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As Corazon gets driven into the corner by Donquixote Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he finally faces Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Corazon takes a chance risking his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a single bullet is shot at him{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which starts the young Law \Non a path towards freedom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Advance, Law! The Kindhearted Man's Final Fight!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.34,0:23:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
